gov.ornl.stucco.entity.models

Class Word

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.ornl.stucco.entity.models.Word

  • public class Word
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an annotated word from a sentence, where the properties include the word itself, its part of speech tag, the I-O-B formatting tag, the domain-specific term assigned to the word, and the probability that the assigned domain term is appropriate.
